casebody.data:
Janosek, Appellee, v. Janosek, Appellant.

[Cite as Janosek v. Janosek, 127 Ohio St.3d 1262, 2010-Ohio-6132.]

(No. 2009-1705 Submitted October 13, 2010 Decided December 20, 2010.) James C. Cochran and Gary S. Singletary, for appellee. Baker & Hostetler, L.L.P., James E. Loeb, David L. Marberger, and Suzanne M. Jambe; and Zukerman, Daiker & Lear Co., L.P.A., Larry W. Zukerman, and Paul B. Daiker, for appellant.

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently accepted.

Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
